                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-96-off551 t18230625-96-crimeloc553"></join>, and felt something at my pocket, which made me turn round. I saw the prisoner close behind me, and another behind him. I seized and charged him with picking my pocket; he denied it, but I saw my handkerchief in his left hand, while I was turning round; he was passing it to his companion, but dropped it. I picked it up, and recognized him, as having attempted my pocket a few hours before - the other went off.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
